<devicesets>
<deviceset name="WE-CNSW_HF_0805" urn="urn:adsk.eagle:component:14282478/1" prefix="L" library_version="1">
<description>&lt;b&gt;WE-CNSW HF SMT Common Mode Line Filter
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;Characteristics 
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;Current compensated data line filter
&lt;br&gt;High common mode noise suppression at high frequencies
&lt;br&gt;Small influence on high speed signals through winding symmetry
&lt;br&gt;Climatic category 40/105/21 (Size 0603)
&lt;br&gt;Climatic category 40/125/21 (Size 0805/1206/1812)
&lt;br&gt;Flammability corresponding to UL 94 V-0
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Applications
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt; USB 3.0 
&lt;br&gt;USB 2.0
&lt;br&gt;HDMI
&lt;br&gt;LVDS
&lt;br&gt;High-Speed data lines
&lt;br&gt;IEEE 1394 (Firewire)
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://katalog.we-online.com/media/images/v2/o35253v209%20Family_we-cnsw_stroko_smd_0805_HF.jpg" title="Enlarge picture"&gt;
&lt;img src="https://katalog.we-online.com/media/images/v2/o35253v209%20Family_we-cnsw_stroko_smd_0805_HF.jpg" width="320"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;
Details see: &lt;a href="http://katalog.we-online.de/en/pbs/WE-CNSW_HF"&gt;http://katalog.we-online.de/en/pbs/WE-CNSW_HF&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;br&gt;Updated  by Ella Wu 2019-01-09&lt;Br&gt;
2019 (C) Wurth Elektronik</description>
