<devicesets>
<deviceset name="WE-TVS-SS_MSOP-8L_82401646" urn="urn:adsk.eagle:component:14283019/4" prefix="D" library_version="6">
<description>&lt;b&gt;WE-TVS TVS Diode – Super Speed Series
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Characteristics
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;Fast turn-on
&lt;br&gt;Low clamping voltage
&lt;br&gt;Very low capacitance
&lt;br&gt;Rail to Rail protection
&lt;br&gt;Small package
&lt;br&gt;Epoxy flame resistant UL94-V0
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Applications
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt; Super Speed data lines
&lt;br&gt;HDMI 1.3/1.4/2.0, DVI
&lt;br&gt;DisplayPort
&lt;br&gt;USB 3.1 Gen 1 (5Gb/s)
&lt;br&gt;SATA and eSATA
&lt;br&gt;GBit LAN
&lt;br&gt;Thunderbolt
&lt;br&gt;LVDS
&lt;br&gt;ESD protection in accordance with EN 61000-4-2 
&lt;br&gt;– 8 kV contact discharge 
&lt;br&gt;– 15 kV air discharge
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;SS = Super Speed
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.we-online.com/catalog/media/o106434v209%20Family_WE-TVS-SuperSpeed.jpg" title="Enlarge picture"&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.we-online.com/catalog/media/o106434v209%20Family_WE-TVS-SuperSpeed.jpg" width="320"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;
Details see: &lt;a href="https://www.we-online.com/catalog/en/WE-TVS-SS"&gt;https://www.we-online.com/catalog/en/WE-TVS-SS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;
Details see: &lt;a href="https://www.we-online.com/catalog/en/WE-TVS-SS"&gt;https://www.we-online.com/catalog/en/WE-TVS-SS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/b&gt;Updated  by Ella Wu 2021-12-16&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/b&gt;2021(C) Wurth Elektronik</description>
